      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/wiapost/5122-Dont-Be-Afraid-Of-Covid.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Don&amp;rsquo;t Be Afraid Of Covid&#34; /&gt;
      
